ğŸš€ Quick Start:
    from vector_math import R2Vector, R3Vector
    
    # Vettori 2D
    v1 = R2Vector(x=3, y=4)
    v2 = R2Vector(x=1, y=2)
    print(v1 + v2)  # R2Vector(x=4, y=6)
    
    # Vettori 3D
    v3 = R3Vector(x=1, y=2, z=3)
    print(v3.norm())  # 3.7416573867739413

